{
  "title": "Одой морь ба уурхай",
  "hidden": true,
  "bodyHtml": "<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Бүрэнхийнгялбаа болорын уурхайгаас нэгэн болор авчээ. Болорын хэмжээ&nbsp;<span style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">n</span>&nbsp;(<span style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">n</span>&nbsp;сондгой;&nbsp;<span id=\"MathJax-Span-9\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">n</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-10\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\"> </span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-11\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.182em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">&gt;</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-12\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\"> </span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-13\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.182em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">1</span>) бол&nbsp;<span id=\"MathJax-Span-16\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">n</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-17\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\"> </span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-18\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.182em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">×</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-19\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\"> </span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-20\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.182em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">n</span>&nbsp;хүснэгтээр илэрхийлж болно.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Танд сондгой бүхэл тоо&nbsp;<span style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">n</span>&nbsp;ѳгѳгдсѳн. Та&nbsp;<span style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">n</span>&nbsp;хэмжээтэй болорыг дүрслэх хэрэгтэй. Уг эрдэнэсийн байрлах хүснэгтийн нүднүүдийг \"<span style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">D</span>\" үсгээр илэрхийлнэ. Бусад нүднүүдийг \"<span style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">∗</span>\" тэмдэгтээр тэмдэглэнэ. Жишээнүүдээс хэрхэн дүрслэх нь ойлгогдох болно.</span></p>\n<h3>Input</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.6000003814697px;\">Ганц мѳрѳнд&nbsp;<span style=\"white-space: nowrap; color: #000000;\">n</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.6000003814697px;\">&nbsp;(<span id=\"MathJax-Span-38\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">3</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-39\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\"> </span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-40\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.182em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">≤</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-41\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\"> </span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-42\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.182em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">n</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-43\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\"> </span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-44\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.182em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">≤</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-45\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\"> </span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-46\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.182em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">101</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.6000003814697px;\">;&nbsp;<span style=\"white-space: nowrap; color: #000000;\">n</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.6000003814697px;\">&nbsp;сондгой) бүхэл тоо байрлана.</span></span></p>\n<h3>Output</h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">n хэмжээтэй болорыг дүрсэл.</span></span></p>\n<h3>Example</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Input 1:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">3</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Output 1:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">*D*<br>DDD<br>*D*</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Input 2:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">5</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Output 2:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">**D**<br>*DDD*<br>DDDDD<br>*DDD*<br>**D**</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Input 3:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">7</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Output 3:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">***D***<br>**DDD**<br>*DDDDD*<br>DDDDDDD<br>*DDDDD*<br>**DDD**<br>***D***</span></p>",
  "bodyText": "Бүрэнхийнгялбаа болорын уурхайгаас нэгэн болор авчээ. Болорын хэмжээ n (n сондгой; n > 1) бол n × n хүснэгтээр илэрхийлж болно.\nТанд сондгой бүхэл тоо n ѳгѳгдсѳн. Та n хэмжээтэй болорыг дүрслэх хэрэгтэй. Уг эрдэнэсийн байрлах хүснэгтийн нүднүүдийг \"D\" үсгээр илэрхийлнэ. Бусад нүднүүдийг \"∗\" тэмдэгтээр тэмдэглэнэ. Жишээнүүдээс хэрхэн дүрслэх нь ойлгогдох болно.\nInput\nГанц мѳрѳнд n (3 ≤ n ≤ 101; n сондгой) бүхэл тоо байрлана.\nOutput\nn хэмжээтэй болорыг дүрсэл.\nExample\nInput 1:\n3\nOutput 1:\n*D*DDD*D*\nInput 2:\n5\nOutput 2:\n**D***DDD*DDDDD*DDD***D**\nInput 3:\n7\nOutput 3:\n***D*****DDD***DDDDD*DDDDDDD*DDDDD***DDD*****D***",
